FuncDef: The reset value-added-service edsg time-range process-information command clears the process of updating the EDSG service bandwidth based on a time range.
ExtraInfo:
Usage Scenario
If the service bandwidth fails to be updated, you can clear the historical service bandwidth update failure records before attempting to reproduce the fault.
Configuration Impact
After the command is run, historical service update failure records are cleared and cannot be restored.
Precautions
In VS mode, this command is supported only by the admin VS.
